---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Book a Discovery Call | OrangeCore Group | Plano, TX"
  description="30-minute discovery call with Glen Swindell. No pitch, no pressure. We'll figure out if a RevOps or fractional CRO engagement makes sense for your company."
>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <div class="eyebrow hero-ey">Book a Call</div>
      <h1>Book a Discovery Call — No Pitch, No Pressure</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">30 minutes with Glen Swindell. We'll figure out together if a RevOps or fractional CRO engagement makes sense for your company. If it doesn't fit, you'll hear that clearly.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-layout fade-in">

        <div class="contact-main">
          <div class="what-to-expect">
            <p class="eyebrow">What to expect</p>
            <h2>Here's what happens on the call.</h2>
            <p>30 minutes. No deck, no pitch. Glen runs it the same way every time:</p>
            <ol class="call-steps">
              <li>
                <span class="step-num">01</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="step-title">You tell us what's going on</p>
                  <p class="step-desc">Revenue situation, team size, what's working, what isn't. No prep needed — just talk through it.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="step-num">02</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="step-title">We tell you honestly what we're seeing</p>
                  <p class="step-desc">Based on what you share, Glen will give you a straight read on whether this looks like a RevOps problem, a fractional CRO situation, or something else entirely.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="step-num">03</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="step-title">We figure out if there's a fit</p>
                  <p class="step-desc">If there is, we'll talk through which engagement makes sense. If there isn't, you'll get honest feedback and walk away with something useful regardless.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="calendly-placeholder fade-in">
            <div class="calendly-box">
              <p class="calendly-label">Schedule your discovery call</p>
              <p class="calendly-sub">Add your Calendly embed link below — replace this block with the Calendly inline widget script when ready.</p>
              <div class="calendly-mock">
                <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--mid-gray);text-align:center;padding:3rem 2rem;">
                  Calendly embed goes here.<br />
                  In production: paste the Calendly inline embed script.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="calendly-fallback">
                <p>Prefer email? Reach Glen directly at <a href="mailto:glen@orangecoregroup.com">glen@orangecoregroup.com</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-sidebar fade-in">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <p class="eyebrow">Who you're talking to</p>
            <div class="glen-block">
              <div class="glen-avatar" aria-label="Glen Swindell">GS</div>
              <div>
                <p class="glen-name">Glen Swindell</p>
                <p class="glen-title">Founder, OrangeCore Group</p>
                <p class="glen-loc">Plano, TX · DFW</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="glen-facts">
              <li>10+ years revenue leadership</li>
              <li>U.S. Army veteran, 2010–2018</li>
              <li>B2B SaaS & fintech focus</li>
              <li>Past clients: Verifone, Bread Financial</li>
              <li>SDVOSB certified</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <p class="eyebrow">Good fit for</p>
            <ul class="fit-list">
              <li>B2B SaaS, fintech, or payments companies</li>
              <li>Post-Series A to mid-market</li>
              <li>Revenue teams without a dedicated CRO</li>
              <li>HubSpot buildout or cleanup needs</li>
              <li>Teams prepping for a board meeting or fundraise</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card sidebar-card--orange">
            <p class="sidebar-note">Based in Plano, TX — available for in-person meetings across DFW. National clients served remotely. Same deliverables, same accountability regardless of location.</p>
            <div class="sdvosb-block">
              <span class="badge">SDVOSB Certified</span>
              <p class="sdvosb-note">Service-Disabled Veteran-Owned Small Business. Qualifies for federal set-aside contracts.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
.hero{background:var(--charcoal);padding:4.5rem 0 3.5rem;text-align:center;}
.hero-ey{color:var(--orange);border:1px solid rgba(232,97,10,0.4);padding:4px 14px;border-radius:2px;}
.hero h1{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,2.8rem);font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-0.03em;max-width:700px;margin:1rem auto 1.25rem;}
.hero-sub{font-size:16px;color:#9A9590;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;font-weight:300;line-height:1.75;}
.contact-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 320px;gap:4rem;align-items:start;}
.what-to-expect{margin-bottom:3rem;}
.what-to-expect h2{font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3vw,1.9rem);margin:0.5rem 0 1rem;}
.what-to-expect>p{font-size:15px;color:var(--mid-gray);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.call-steps{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;}
.call-steps li{display:flex;gap:1.5rem;padding:1.25rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);align-items:flex-start;}
.call-steps li:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.step-num{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--orange);opacity:0.5;flex-shrink:0;min-width:28px;}
.step-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:0.3rem;}
.step-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--mid-gray);line-height:1.6;}
.calendly-box{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;}
.calendly-label{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--charcoal);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem 0;}
.calendly-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--mid-gray);padding:0.25rem 1.5rem 0;line-height:1.5;}
.calendly-mock{background:var(--warm-gray);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:1rem;min-height:260px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.calendly-fallback{padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;}
.calendly-fallback p{font-size:13px;color:var(--mid-gray);}
.calendly-fallback a{color:var(--orange);font-weight:500;}
.calendly-fallback a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
.sidebar-card{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;}
.sidebar-card--orange{background:var(--orange-light);border-color:var(--orange-mid);}
.glen-block{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin:1rem 0;}
.glen-avatar{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--charcoal);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
.glen-name{font-weight:500;font-size:15px;color:var(--charcoal);}
.glen-title{font-size:12px;color:var(--mid-gray);}
.glen-loc{font-size:12px;color:var(--mid-gray);}
.glen-facts{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.4rem;}
.glen-facts li{font-size:13px;color:var(--mid-gray);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.glen-facts li:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.glen-facts li::before{content:'✓';color:var(--green);font-weight:600;font-size:12px;flex-shrink:0;}
.fit-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.4rem;margin-top:0.75rem;}
.fit-list li{font-size:13px;color:var(--charcoal);display:flex;gap:8px;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.fit-list li:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.fit-list li::before{content:'→';color:var(--orange);flex-shrink:0;}
.sidebar-note{font-size:13px;color:var(--charcoal);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:1.25rem;}
.sdvosb-block{border-top:1px solid var(--orange-mid);padding-top:1rem;}
.badge{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid rgba(232,97,10,0.4);color:var(--orange);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;}
.sdvosb-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--mid-gray);line-height:1.5;}
@media(max-width:768px){.contact-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
</style>
